Type: Package
Package: pombesize
Title: Single-Cell Fission Yeast Size and Geometry
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Istvan", "Kleijn", , "istvankleijn@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9466-9167"))
Description: Size and geometry data of 1242 Schizosaccharomyces pombe
    cells across 25 growth conditions. The included cell size measures are
    length, width, surface area, and volume. Also provides details about
    the culture conditions that the cells were grown in, and summary
    statistics of the single-cell data set grouped by culture condition.
